dy">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">imap</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/class.imap-connection.php" class="classname">IMAP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受有效的 <span>imap</span> <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="link">resource</a>。 </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.imap-lsub-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_list()} - Read the list of mailboxes</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_getmailboxes()} - Read the list of mailboxes, returning detailed information on each one</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
